WLSH","ref":"1Cor.9.3","text":"Mine answer to them that do examine me is this,","year":59},{"id":"recXNE4yDk8Oh2ywS","ref":"1Cor.9.4","text":"Have we not power to eat and to drink?","year":59},{"id":"rec87Xc14oOuqBq8K","ref":"1Cor.9.5","text":"Have we not power to lead about a sister, a wife, as well as other apostles, and as the brethren of the Lord, and Cephas?","year":59},{"id":"recHq5yRAmA5C1QS7","ref":"1Cor.9.6","text":"Or I only and Barnabas, have not we power to forbear working?","year":59},{"id":"recnun9c50iMeIv0v","ref":"1Cor.9.7","text":"Who goeth a warfare any time at his own charges? who planteth a vineyard, and eateth not of the fruit thereof? or who feedeth a flock, and eateth not of the milk of the flock?","year":59},{"id":"recnsL3t1VktIObg4","ref":"1Cor.9.8","text":"Say I these things as a man? or saith not the law the same also?","year":59}]}
